author: Geoff Earle
title: U.S. officials verify some of Trump dirty dossier | Daily Mail Online
text: Parts of Trump 'dirty dossier' HAVE been verified by investigators - but NOT the most salacious details including 'golden shower' claims Government investigators have verified some elements of a 'dirty dossier' of information on President Trump, CNN reported The information relates to communications between Russian individuals and the Russian government Investigators have not corroborated 'salacious' details in the dossier or revealed specific information that has been confirmed A former British intelligence officer compiled a 35-page dossier of financial and personal dirt on Trump, but it hasn't been verified It was fist published by Buzzfeed before elements of it got discredited Published: 00:34 GMT, 11 February 2017 | Updated: 04:32 GMT, 11 February 2017 332 shares
